{"tid":2318415,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Google Pay 呢?] 華為與八達通合作推出流動支付服務","createTime":"2020-12-09T10:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:15:04.000Z","uid":34550,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbd6b99fbbc1d16e782060584f4e9c9702c399e","tid":2318415,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/files/images/20201209154636_201209155123_m.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2F20201209154636_201209155123_m.JPG&h=91169628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為香港與八達通合作推出Huawei Pay八達通流動支付服務. 即日起, 用戶可使用華為手機, 於全港10萬個八達通覆蓋點進行支付, 無須將手機解鎖或開啟任何應用程式, 隻需將支援NFC的華為手機輕觸八達通讀寫器, 可支付交通以及多項日常消費.<br />\n        Huawei Pay屬華為流動服務 (HUAWEI Mobile Services, HMS)的其中一項主要服務, 華為消費者業務大中華區副總裁何鴻略表示, 在本港, 消費者愈來愈接受HMS平台, 推出Huawei Pay八達通服務, 標誌著HMS在香港發展進入新裏程, 為手機用戶帶來方便及安全的支付體驗.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20201209154636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20201209154636&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=98ddfbec\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20201209154636</a>"},{"pid":"0b21797e9ef6bb2cc56d86766932e3f9c80330d3","tid":2318415,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">無須將手機解鎖或開啟任何應用程式</code></pre><br />\n可以買部嘢任嘟人哋張八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaebd0eddf9ba43b010255b90729d3fad11a9dc","tid":2318415,"uid":216417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b21797e9ef6bb2cc56d86766932e3f9c80330d3","tid":2318415,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">無須將手機解鎖或開啟任何應用程式</code></pre><br />\n可以買部嘢任嘟人哋